dct_title_s: Map of the Toussaint Creek Basin and the adjacent Lake Erie tributaries showing availability of underground water
dct_alternative_sm: Ohio water plan inventory. Underground water resources. Toussaint Creek Basin and adjacent Lake Erie tributaries
dct_description_sm: Prepared by RUSSELL B. STEIN, Geologist, Ohio Division of Water
Map side also contains legend and explanation of map symbols.
Text includes information about generalized stratigraphic sequence of rocks in Toussaint Creek area and the quality of underground water.
